{"type":"message","id":"91c7a28b","parentId":"e30da4f3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:49:00.264Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_og62hpq52o9j_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"azhua-skill-vetter\ncapability-evolver\njx76-gog\nmiaoda-doc-parse\nmiaoda-image-understanding\nmiaoda-speech-to-text\nmiaoda-text-gen-image\nmiaoda-web-fetch\nmiaoda-web-search\nplaywright\nweda-connector"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"azhua-skill-vetter\ncapability-evolver\njx76-gog\nmiaoda-doc-parse\nmiaoda-image-understanding\nmiaoda-speech-to-text\nmiaoda-text-gen-image\nmiaoda-web-fetch\nmiaoda-web-search\nplaywright\nweda-connector","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775076540260}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2a47a59","parentId":"91c7a28b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:49:03.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The miaoda-web-search skill is at `/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md`. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"5640dd271c90474736c9cf9a12d7c9c353e10b71b042ab83cedc7398925fa97e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oti0e5nm6m9q_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1044,"output":78,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45103,"cost":{"input":0.00031319999999999997,"output":0.0000936,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017262299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775076540263}}
{"type":"message","id":"9db4d4a9","parentId":"a2a47a59","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:49:03.533Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_oti0e5nm6m9q_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775076543530}}
{"type":"message","id":"26480019","parentId":"9db4d4a9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:49:08.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I know how to use the web search. Let me search for latest information on the relevant industries for 道简网络.","thinkingSignature":"3b767502a8f28968ff5348d50697fe33880b58987859699fff16adef10f9c33f"},{"type":"text","text":"搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lm1fwu956il2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lm1fwu956il2_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 行业动态 2026\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lm1fwu956il2_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 网络系统集成 行业发展趋势 2026\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1637,"output":173,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45791,"cost":{"input":0.0004911,"output":0.00020759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00201813}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775076543533}}
